      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a preserved example of the ultimate driving machine. Powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L I6, it features a documented rod bearing replacement and comprehensive VANOS service. The rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced for structural longevity. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. The suspension geometry is stock and tight, providing the signature telepathic steering feel. With zero paint imperfections and an interior devoid of bolster wear, this specimen represents the pinnacle of E46 preservation.",
